<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She enjoyed a romantic dinner date night with Kanye West next to a massive tent structure, lit by the lights of their car.</p>

<p>And one day later, Kim Kardashian shared a series of sweet snaps of her four kids plus one with their dad Kanye.</p>

<p>The 39-year-old captioned the adorable images she shared Tuesday with: 'How did I get so lucky?!?!?!'</p>

<p>Family first: Kim Kardashian shared a series of sweet snaps of her four kids plus one with their dad Kanye on Tuesday morning</p>

<p>Kim and Kanye are parents to four kids: daughters North, seven, and Chicago, two, and sons Saint, four, and Psalm, one year.</p>

<p>In the images, North donned a purple sweater with taupe colored slides and her hair up in twin buns.</p>

<p>In several of the images, she was holding her younger brother Psalm in her arms; the toddler donned a neutral hued top with matching bottoms.</p>

<p>Saint rocked a camouflage patterned top with neon shorts and slides while sister Chicago wore similar colors for her tee and overalls look. </p>

<p>One image showed Kanye smiling as he crouched down near Psalm, with another pictured featuring North with Chicago. </p>

<p>Doting mom: The 39-year-old captioned the adorable images she shared Tuesday with: 'How did I get so lucky?!?!?!</p>

